{"tid":1630882,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"見到有人言論唔多對路，多d 起底","createTime":"2019-10-06T14:00:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T14:50:38.000Z","uid":73945,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"dcb586f6cbdecfdea1592b74576a60e3ccf4f8dc","tid":1630882,"uid":73945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:00:30.000Z","msg":"如果你見到有人開post 或者回覆講既野唔多妥<br />\n起佢底好多時會發現至少三個月沒講過野<br />\n甚至開account 後完全沒post 過<br />\n<br />\n呢幾日鬼account 帶風向post 多到仆街<br />\n<br />\n通常唔多講野既user, 忽然開聲多數因為d 好重要既野，唔會附和一句咁簡單<br />\n發表長篇大論既，六月以黎應該一路都出過聲，唔會到十月先黎第一篇文<br />\n<br />\n有時唔駛懷疑自己諗錯野<br />\n見到相反意見既post, 起底完來鬼account 黎<br />\n就會發現唔係自己諗錯，而係有人帶風向洗正評"},{"pid":"a96b4b868990f6f1bbb206a7c21ebdcc6aa9b65d","tid":1630882,"uid":57073,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:02:09.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n多數 2 3 個P 牌喺到帶風向"},{"pid":"04dd16db7ce08b25fd276878d39f3e636078879d","tid":1630882,"uid":154486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:03:44.000Z","msg":"唔只P牌<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nMynjQN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnMynjQN.jpg&h=cce388ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z1TKyaO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz1TKyaO.jpg&h=cce4fd80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O7rL139.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO7rL139.jpg&h=26b5d5ac&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e1f400021b574e93550799bc1b3bfc2e0dd76642","tid":1630882,"uid":73945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a96b4b868990f6f1bbb206a7c21ebdcc6aa9b65d","tid":1630882,"uid":57073,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:02:09.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n多數 2 3 個P 牌喺到帶風向"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:50:38.000Z","msg":"有d 舊account 似係以前已經有既打手<br />\n亦可能係被捕者手機畀人拿咗去用"}]}